
Todays Soft Skill Tip:

Day 26 – Interview Follow-Up: Win With Professionalism

The interview isn’t over when you leave.

A crisp thank-you note shows maturity, recall, and genuine interest.

It also keeps you top-of-mind.

* Thank them for the opportunity
* One line recalling a topic discussed
* One line on how you can contribute

Use this as your template and create your Follow up message 
